cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with face recognition using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks to learn a non-linear mapping also suggests that it could fall under machine learning (cs.MM) or deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves training the model to preserve identity information, which could be considered an artificial intelligence (cs.AI) problem. Finally, the use of neural networks for this task suggests that it could also fall under neural networks (cs.NE).
